								<div class="title" id="post-title-3626234">
																		...I never said she didn&#039;t have a robot hand.
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drchandra" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1956625); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1956625&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610164535" alt="DrChandra" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1956625)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drchandra" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1956625); return false;" >DrChandra</a></span> <span class="odate time_1509832781 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">04 Nov 2017 21:59</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3626234">
									

<p>To paraphrase <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-751251/alternate-character-interpretations">IHP</a>, I'd like to thank <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/randomini" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1379080); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1379080&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1509832780" alt="Randomini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1379080)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/randomini" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1379080); return false;">Randomini</a></span> for letting me mangle his character to an unrecognizable degree.</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Click&nbsp;here&nbsp;for&nbsp;a&nbsp;wall&nbsp;of&nbsp;text&nbsp;about&nbsp;canon</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">If&nbsp;nothing&nbsp;is&nbsp;canon,&nbsp;then&nbsp;everything&nbsp;is&nbsp;canon...</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>When I posted my first Iris Dark article a couple months ago, Wills and Ways hadn't been added to in a year and a half, and that was about a year and a half after the previous addition. I was reasonably sure it was dead. I knew I was reimagining Iris to an extent, but I thought that maybe there was enough open to interpretation for her to still be the Iris from W&amp;W, and that Dread &amp; Circuses could then be part of the Acidverse, as I have also incorporated the Utterly Bazaar pretty strongly into the story-line.</p>
<p>Though Randomini has been very gracious and not taken issue with me writing an alternative version of his character, he has also made it very clear that she <em>is</em> an alternate version, and that neither my portrayal of her nor the events she participates in are congruent with his continuity. Now that he has resumed writing Wills and Ways I feel a little awkward simultaneously writing about an alternate version of his character, but fortunately for me Randomini is okay with it.</p>
<p>I just want to make it clear to everyone that my Iris is a different Iris from Randomini's Iris. Since she's the Iris of Dread &amp; Circuses, I shall call her Dread Iris. This also means that Dread &amp; Circuses is now officially a separate canon from Acidverse. My Marshall (even though I avoided naming him, it was Amos Marshall who showed up in <em>She Remembered Me</em>) and my Carter (though he hasn't shown up yet) are mostly the same as W&amp;W's, but Randomini has also said that my Darke is very different from his Darke.</p>
<p>Something similar to Wills and Ways still happened in Dread and Circuses, but there will be some point of clear divergence. I don't know what will happen to W&amp;W Iris, but Dread Iris became Darke's proxy and apprentice while remaining his heir. Dread Iris was also definitely aware of her heritage prior to the assassination and had at least some previous interactions with Darke.</p>
<p>I will incorporate future developments in Wills and Ways as I see fit, and when Iris shows up again in Dread &amp; Circuses I'll probably mention she has a robot hand.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>Anyway, thanks to my beta readers <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/freemayne" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3046692); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3046692&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1509832780" alt="Freemayne" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3046692)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/freemayne" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3046692); return false;">Freemayne</a></span> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/modern-erasmus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3129691); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3129691&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1509832780" alt="Modern_Erasmus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3129691)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/modern-erasmus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3129691); return false;">Modern_Erasmus</a></span> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/superblobby" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2008009); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2008009&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1509832780" alt="Superblobby" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2008009)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/superblobby" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2008009); return false;">Superblobby</a></span> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ekronak" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3409685); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3409685&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1509832780" alt="Ekronak" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3409685)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ekronak" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3409685); return false;">Ekronak</a></span> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/not-a-seagull" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3009022); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3009022&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1509832780" alt="not_a_seagull" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3009022)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/not-a-seagull" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3009022); return false;">not_a_seagull</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/srgunk" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3354258); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3354258&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1509832780" alt="SrGunk" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3354258)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/srgunk" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3354258); return false;">SrGunk</a></span>.</p>

