			<div class="content" id="post-content-3626319">
									

<p>My response would be that the Serpent's Hand is not a coherent organization. It's more of a political/ideological leaning. If you identify as Serpent's Hand, then you are Serpent's Hand, and there's no command structure telling people what to do.</p>
<p>I'm sure that there are member's of the Serpent's Hand that think this is a terrible idea, but others want a safe place to share and store secret info and network with fellow members, so they decide it's worth the risk.</p>
